[thinking] **Considering Kafka integration**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m looking at enhancing coverage in my Kafka setup. The KafkaExpressionEvaluatingInterceptor can add the message key header, while the KafkaNullConverter might need a method to convert KafkaNull to null. I also want to ensure the DefaultMessageConverterHelper is set up for batch header prunes, and there are runtime hints for properties.
[thinking] 
[thinking] I have to think about merging broker configurations, provisioning topics, and using Spring Integration's DirectChannel for binding producers and consumers. I wonder how to effectively configure this with Spring Boot and whether additional dependencies will be necessary.
[thinking] 
