[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering Kafka integration**\n\nI’m looking at enhancing coverage in my Kafka setup. The KafkaExpressionEvaluatingInterceptor can add the message key header, while the KafkaNullConverter might need a method to convert KafkaNull to null. I also want to ensure the DefaultMessageConverterHelper is set up for batch header prunes, and there are runtime hints for properties.\n\nI have to think about merging broker configurations, provisioning topics, and using Spring Integration's DirectChannel for binding producers and consumers. I wonder how to effectively configure this with Spring Boot and whether additional dependencies will be necessary.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_007c0874e003665f016a404180cd408194abd93e504bfaac0d\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQEGJeg4lkYHvLP7_Fr8QN_ozONb5Z4mJCGb9u6cjcia_Z8U6FppOmbkVG_XMdWxQQj7WKWQpPx1UrJCGWKsp8ORGcYvdg1x5BgA4YcHMd5KySMzk6cESEG2mh3hXVdSISnYQwiNXKsMYuXrQQaOP7EGFqw1sPkYCrjtRvMaVtOGZE0rZ6eoY7OPn_xaTGz1V3vatgbV3DM98imwei3zQNvCWk_k5FxtLd1vXtXEeEJ-vcR_dghjGtYrgtJPNQ_DjLEFNKxgGW-PIjl7WHJfOxoxY4spV6_4KIPoxp9TIYISKmE9P6OQQc5gXdOkgxWkiQbxlcTdNx13ayCv_l2dcuGYIf3AERb3_9IcsjNkf8RZ3xiQH_hhNHW7TAE5_sXdEPbQAhpEJ9in9ZqoWJSbmv6jCr4cUUJWqEAUq-1SGJ0-LuX_fomoJ5nbnXxHEDvVn6nTkRmFxqb5Rq3-D822ENWHzJkmzFyuMZwtQ6CjgGF_6BnzCbRSDOENWsFoD-WbZ3xCZjVz8_PuhU1rL6nTL0Q3uqxOSS-TZ6Kd3GMHk5FZm14IuhPGwl_PeWqT78IyVFurVgo6lt57QI4HRPO47UA5v1IfPZYKRyonTMxclTluBkQ5_ysydq5v6UsjX1lSxR3xa-n1tt1MWMGK208gnSLmhSWxsRe-0MdNNoXBLCtlv68lFhjSu6VmgP8_w_IzxyFD95bIwv6kRJ-aKL97TO96TTx14rqZ_9oclxsU0yMwpX8OMxo2pb5P0D9G6kVv4bspr7GRIvrJL1ysOQHV_b3Yuxe7hyxrFyGVSvB7M2RBIxtIxew6jbMYim8vcuyoFU2HM6-f6JhmJ7jFJwLjKoOX8IGNNBWzx3gnSm0RhdH7WT2FVw_iAmn-jVji_9UmV_vLDMTSZ96fol_j5qS2lT-SHZCnPWVU2GGQ1PQnX-qIjC6z3-YuqO_Q3Z2cGs2nHQHylblXcH7p7vUievTjTu3Nf4FKGJGCz8BlctpYZOwWM35AAebCP8hUejtSGlDgfCSX8Q1jkUN0eBOnidbbmPTLv9ayIHcwpjlvNl4pjs9gO0aOYwb9HSMV42P